This program uses threads and semaphores to demonstrate the reader/writer problem and uses 4 readers and 4 writers.

Multiple simultaneous readers are allowed. A writer will block any other writers and readers while its writing.

Readers will block writers from writing until they are done reading.


Author: Frankie Gauthier
CS3790 Assign2



HOW TO RUN
----------

type make in the java directory to compile and link the program

type "java JavaSemaphores" to run the program


CLONE
-------
github url

type git clone "https://github.com/frgauthi/CS3790Assign2"


